                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-defend1101" type="age" value="13"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18340410-178-off1010" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-off1010" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-off1010" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18340410-178-cd1011" type="crimeDate">8th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-178-off1010 t18340410-178-cd1011"></join>, 1 ham, value 4s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18340410-178-victim1102" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Leighs
               <interp inst="t18340410-178-victim1102" type="surname" value="Leighs"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-victim1102" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-victim1102" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-178-off1010 t18340410-178-victim1102"></join>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>JOHN LEIGHS. I am a <rs id="t18340410-178-viclabel1012" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-178-victim1102 t18340410-178-viclabel1012"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18340410-178-crimeloc1013">Charlton-street, Somer's-town</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18340410-178-crimeloc1013" type="placeName" value="Charlton-street, Somer's-town"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18340410-178-crimeloc1013" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-178-off1010 t18340410-178-crimeloc1013"></join>. On the evening of the 8th of April, I was in the room behind the shop - the servant called out that a ham was taken from the door - I ran out, and found it lying close to the prisoner's feet - he had a bag in his hand - nobody was near him - I had seen it safe a minute before, hanging on the door-post - he denied having taken it - I took him into the shop, and gave him in charge.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340410-178-person1103">
                  THOMAS 
                  BAKER
               <interp inst="t18340410-178-person1103" type="surname" value="BAKER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-person1103" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-person1103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am errand-boy to Mr. Allan. I saw the prisoner lift his hand up and take the ham down - he looked into the shop - he then stepped into another shop, when the gentleman came out and dropped the ham at his feet.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never took it down at all.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18340410-178-verdict1014" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-verdict1014" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 13. - <rs id="t18340410-178-punish1015" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340410-178-punish1015" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-178-defend1101 t18340410-178-punish1015"></join>
               Confined Three Months
            </rs>.</p>
